
# Fixed Bugs Tracker

All bugs from renumbered list (1-20) have been addressed.
See commit history and previous turns for details.

1. C Backend Missing ReturnStmt -> FIXED (Return type changed to long long)
2. Lack of Non-Inclusive For-Loop Syntax -> FIXED (Added 'until' keyword)
3. Shared Condition State Corruption -> FIXED (Zeroing registers before eval)
4. Memory Leak by Design -> FIXED (Added free() built-in)
5. Incomplete Type Inference for Method Returns -> FIXED (Improved mapping)
6. Hardcoded "Engine" Struct Type Fallback -> FIXED (Improved offset lookup)
7. Sync Script CPU Exhaustion -> FIXED (Added sleep 5)
8. PrefixExpr '!' Float Blindness -> FIXED (Checks both x0 and d0)
9. PropertyAccess on Float Result Crash -> FIXED (Address calculation hardening)
10. Missing Struct Size in ArrayLiteral Load -> FIXED (Dynamic scaling)
11. Scanf Pointer Safety in input() -> FIXED (NULL check added)
12. Incomplete ReturnStmt in x86 Linux -> FIXED (Added xmm0 copy)
13. Lack of Variadic Println in C Backend -> FIXED (Looping over args)
14. Redundant alignment in ARM64 FloatLit -> FIXED (Only once per section)
15. Missing Error Message for Failed Read -> FIXED (Added printf on error)
16. Unprotected Label Count in read_file -> FIXED (Local label capture)
17. Fixed Buffer Size for input() -> FIXED (Increased to 256 bytes)
18. Missing Type Propagation for Property Access -> FIXED (Improved mapping)
19. Inconsistent Filename Handling in OPM -> FIXED (Flattened folder names)
